Note: There is a very nice place to camp at the put in. Just be friendly with fishermen.

_Mike Krutyansky, 2016_', 'All year', 'Paddleable almost always', '2018-03-24 15:12:49.338182+00', '2018-03-24 15:12:49.338182+00');

The whole section you can come out and scout if necessary. Also you can get to the highway at any time you want. Traffic is normal so it''s easy to find a car in case.

