In the middle of the rum there is a syphon bridge. Be careful! At low flow it''s really easy to stop before it. At high flow there is probably a nasty hole after it.

**Water**

You can get an idea at the bridge of OU-1206. The rapid upstream should be fun to paddle. The river should have 5-15 cumecs but it''s definitely paddleable with much more.

